    <item>
      <title>斯塔默试图在关键之年压制包括马斯克在内的批评者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-04/starmer-seeks-to-stifle-critics-including-musk-in-pivotal-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相凯尔·斯塔默在新年伊始对他的团队做出了明确的指示：保持冷静，压制反对者的声音，专注于为英国民众服务。但工党内部一些人质疑，这种稳扎稳打的做法是否足以抵御 2025 年的逆风。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-04/starmer-seeks-to-stifle-critics-including-musk-in-pivotal-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Jan 2025 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将禁止在美国大西洋和太平洋大片水域进行新的石油钻探</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-04/biden-to-ban-new-oil-drilling-over-vast-stretch-of-us-atlantic-pacific-waters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将下令禁止在美国沿海约 6.25 亿英亩的土地上进行新的海上石油和天然气开发，并禁止出售大西洋和太平洋水域以及墨西哥湾东部的钻探权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-04/biden-to-ban-new-oil-drilling-over-vast-stretch-of-us-atlantic-pacific-waters</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Jan 2025 04:08:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市拥堵收费制度获法官批准，将于周日开始实施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-04/nyc-congestion-pricing-cleared-by-judge-for-sunday-launch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约一项备受争议的计划，即对进入曼哈顿中央商务区的司机收取费用，已获得联邦法官批准，并于周日生效。此举对邻近的新泽西州取消交通拥堵收费的努力造成了打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-04/nyc-congestion-pricing-cleared-by-judge-for-sunday-launch</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Jan 2025 01:42:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对自己挑选的中东和平特使团队不太满意</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-04/trump-is-not-enamored-with-morgan-ortagus-his-pick-for-mideast-peace-team</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当当选总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布他选择第二号中东和平特使时，他明确表示他对此并不感到兴奋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-04/trump-is-not-enamored-with-morgan-ortagus-his-pick-for-mideast-peace-team</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Jan 2025 00:25:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法部请求最高法院驳回特朗普推迟 TikTok 禁令的请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/doj-asks-supreme-court-to-reject-trump-bid-to-delay-tiktok-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府建议最高法院拒绝唐纳德·特朗普的请求，即推迟一项法律的实施，该法律规定，如果 TikTok 不被其中国母公司出售，该法律将禁止 TikTok 在美国运营。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/doj-asks-supreme-court-to-reject-trump-bid-to-delay-tiktok-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 23:13:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉斯维加斯爆炸案凶手患有创伤后应激障碍，不是恐怖袭击嫌疑人：FBI</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/las-vegas-bomber-suffered-ptsd-and-isn-t-terror-suspect-fbi-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[执法官员称，元旦当天，拉斯维加斯特朗普国际酒店外的爆炸事件中丧生的一位美国陆军绿色贝雷帽士兵患有创伤后应激障碍，并且与恐怖主义没有明显关联。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/las-vegas-bomber-suffered-ptsd-and-isn-t-terror-suspect-fbi-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 23:01:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新日铁拒绝表明国家安全意味着一切</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/nippon-rejection-shows-national-security-means-whatever-you-want</link>
      <description><![CDATA[（彭博社）——几个月来，美国钢铁公司一直认为，将公司出售给日本新日铁公司是唯一的生存之道。但拜登总统却不这么认为，他认为，即使是被一家总部位于亲密盟友日本的公司收购，也不足以缓解国家安全担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/nippon-rejection-shows-national-security-means-whatever-you-want</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 22:27:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普未能推翻纽约州的定罪，将于 1 月 10 日接受宣判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/trump-loses-latest-bid-to-overturn-new-york-criminal-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普已被要求于 1 月 10 日出庭接受封口费刑事案件的宣判，但纽约州法官表示这位当选总统不会入狱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/trump-loses-latest-bid-to-overturn-new-york-criminal-conviction</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 20:57:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>约翰逊在与反对派进行最后谈判后赢得众议院议长选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/johnson-wins-house-speaker-vote-after-late-talks-with-holdouts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党人迈克·约翰逊在经过最后一刻的一系列谈判后，克服了少数但至关重要的保守派强硬派的阻力，并得到了当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的关键支持，再次当选众议院议长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/johnson-wins-house-speaker-vote-after-late-talks-with-holdouts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 19:35:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽森严厉打击加工食品，呼应罗伯特·肯尼迪的焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/newsom-targets-highly-processed-foods-echoing-rfk-jr-priority</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州州长加文·纽瑟姆下令严厉打击与健康风险有关的食品添加剂，反映出两党对高度加工饮食对公众健康造成的损害的担忧日益加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/newsom-targets-highly-processed-foods-echoing-rfk-jr-priority</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
